    "title": "关于修订《京东开放平台运动户外类目资质标准》的公示通知",
    "followRuleId": "1224987876748562432",
    "content": "<p class=\"sl-paragraph sl-indent1\" style=\"text-indent: 4em; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">尊敬的商家/供应商朋友：</span></p>\n<p class=\"sl-paragraph sl-indent1\" style=\"text-indent: 4em; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">您好，为适应业务发展需求，将针对《京东开放平台运动户外类目资质标准》进行调整。现进行规则公示，公示期：2025年4月16日- 2025年4月22日，规则预计于 2025年4月23日生效，公示期满平台将另行发布正式生效规则。</span></p>\n<p class=\"sl-paragraph sl-indent1\" style=\"text-indent: 4em; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">核心调整点：</span></p>\n<table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" style=\"width: 100.0%; border-collapse: collapse;\" border=\"0\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height: 14.5pt;\">\n<td style=\"width: 12.48%; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; background: #C00000; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 14.5pt;\" width=\"12%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei Light', sans-serif; color: white;\">#</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 23.26%; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-left: none; background: #C00000; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 14.5pt;\" width=\"23%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei Light', sans-serif; color: white;\">调整点</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 32.38%; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-left: none; background: #C00000; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 14.5pt;\" width=\"32%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei Light', sans-serif; color: white;\">修订前</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 31.9%; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-left: none; background: #C00000; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 14.5pt;\" width=\"31%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei Light', sans-serif; color: white;\">修订后</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 130.0pt;\">\n<td style=\"width: 12.48%; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-top: none; background: white; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 130.0pt;\" width=\"12%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei Light', sans-serif; color: black;\">1</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 23.26%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 130.0pt;\" width=\"23%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei Light', sans-serif; color: black;\">取消阿迪耐克品牌的邀约入驻限制，调整其余的品牌的入驻授权层级要求</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 32.38%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 130.0pt;\" width=\"32%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei Light', sans-serif; color: black;\">Adidas/</span><span style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei Light', sans-serif; color: black;\">阿迪达斯、NIKE/耐克品牌采取邀约入驻。CONVERSE/匡威、NEW BALANCE/新百伦、ASICS/亚瑟士、UNDERARMOUR/安德玛、Onitsuka Tiger/鬼冢虎、VANS/万斯、PUMA/彪马品牌开设专卖店、专营店、卖场店需有2级以内（包括2级）的完整授权链路。</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 31.9%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 130.0pt;\" width=\"31%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei Light', sans-serif; color: black;\">Adidas/</span><span style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei Light', sans-serif; color: black;\">阿迪达斯、NIKE/耐克和NEW BALANCE开设专卖店、专营店、卖场店需有2级以内（包括2级）的完整授权链路。其余品牌开设专卖店、专营店、卖场店需有3级以内（包括3级）的完整授权链路。</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 117.0pt;\">\n<td style=\"width: 12.48%; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-top: none; background: white; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 117.0pt;\" width=\"12%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei Light', sans-serif; color: black;\">2</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 23.26%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 117.0pt;\" width=\"23%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei Light', sans-serif; color: black;\">授权材料放宽</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 32.38%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 117.0pt;\" width=\"32%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei Light', sans-serif; color: black;\">专卖店、专营店需有3级以内（包括3级）的完整授权链路。</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 31.9%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; background: white; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 117.0pt;\" width=\"31%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei Light', sans-serif; color: black;\">授权链路包括开店授权书、零售商许可证、合作协议、发票等。但开设旗舰店、专卖店必须是品牌（商标）权利人或者是持有由品牌权利人发起的完整授链的京东销售授权书。其他授权形式仅可开设专营店或卖场店。</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>",
